short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension shows off information about the Disquad Community and links to Disquad social media.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is a simple Google Chrome Extension for the Disquad Community. It allows users to easily keep an eye on the top 10 most active members of Disquad as well as give easy access to the full Disquad Leaderboard and Disquad Social Media.
